video.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso
video.synopsis: Catalina starts working out around the neighborhood to get in shape, but what she really wants are breast implants.

episodes.synopsis: Catalina works out in the neighborhood to tone her body. She is anxious to undergo another breast enhancement procedure.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: With Hilda's children gone, Albeiro stays with her at her house. He spies on her that night, aroused by the sight of her body.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Bairon hides in his house after being shot at. Mariño offers five million pesos in exchange for Catalina's virginity.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Albeiro asks Catalina to move in with him but she refuses. Catalina starts to show signs of being pregnant; Jessica lends her money for an abortion.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Jessica gets 30 women to go to Morón's birthday. Catalina and the other women arrive at the farm where Morón's party is to be held.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: The guards find Caballo's body in the barn. Meanwhile, Catalina tells Cardona that Orlando murdered Caballo.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Catalina tells Albeiro she loves him but insists they cannot be a couple again. Cardona continues to pay Catalina to be his lover.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Catalina is upset when Cardona flees the country without leaving her any money for her operation. Catalina and Bairon talk about their real work.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: Catalina and Jessica look for clinics that do breast implant procedures. Catalina gets a quote from Dr. Mauricio and tries to haggle over the price.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: The police stop two men from attacking Catalina and Jessica on the street. Jessica and Catalina take refuge in the police station for the night.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Hilda declares her love to Albeiro. Catalina celebrates her birthday with family and friends. Hilda cries when she sees Albeiro and Catalina together.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Catalina gets Albeiro drunk so he won't realize that she's no longer a virgin. Hilda is distraught over Albeiro and Catalina's love affair.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Jessica and Catalina wait every day at the clinic for Mauricio to return. Catalina finds him and undergoes surgery again.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Jessica takes care of Catalina, who is recovering from her surgery. Mauricio examines Catalina and removes her stitches.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: Jessica sets up Catalina with the richest men in the country. Drunk, Albeiro tells Octavio what he has been through with Catalina.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: Catalina convinces Albeiro that she didn't do anything wrong in the city; they make love. Hilda punishes Catalina for spending the night with Albeiro.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: Catalina accepts Marcial's proposal that they live together. Marcial eavesdrops on Catalina and Jessica thanks to the hidden cameras and microphones.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: Catalina loses her crown. Bonifacio returns the money to Marcial for failing to fulfill his pact that Catalina would win the pageant.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: Catalina and Jessica hide from Pelambre and stay in Pereira. Back at Marcial's house, Catalina and Jessica make up excuses about where they've been..
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: Pelambre photographs Catalina with Albeiro and shows Marcial the photgraphs. Marcial asks Pelambre to kill Albeiro.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: They remove Catalina's breast implants due to her delicate state of health. Dr. Molina confesses to Catalina that they are poor quality implants.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: Pelambre calls Marcial to give him the news about Catalina. Catalina is informed that she won't be able to receive implants for the next two years.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: Catalina finds out about Marcial and Jessica's love affair, so she decides to call Jessica to lure her into a deadly trap.
episodes.title: Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso: Episode 23
